        <briefdescription>
<para>Ready state handler function for timer expired events. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para><hruler/>
</para>
<para><simplesect kind="return"><para>The state ID of the idle state</para>
</simplesect>
The function print a debug message at warning level, perform a sleep of 3 seconds to wait for the final debug messages and perform a reset by calling function sys_reboot provided by Zephyr library API. The return statement will never reached. </para>
        </detaileddescription>
