    <briefdescription>
<para>Ready state class derived from base class <ref refid="class_fw_state" kindref="compound">FwState</ref>. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><hruler/>
</para>
<para><simplesect kind="par"><title>Detailed Description </title><para>The ready state class overrides the handler function of timer expired events. In this state the download has been finished successfully and a reset has to be performed. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
